# Changelog


## [0.0.2] - 2025-03-29

### Added
- 📄 Added `LICENSE` file under MIT License
- 📝 Created comprehensive `README.md` with usage examples, features, and setup instructions


## [0.0.1] - 2025-03-29

### Added
- 🎉 Initial release of `@eliandsantos/phone-input-lib`
- International phone number input component for Angular
- Country selector with dial codes
- Automatic formatting based on country standards
- Phone number validation (min length by country)
- Responsive layout and customizable styling via CSS variables
- Shadow DOM encapsulation
- Exported pipes: `InternationalPhonePipe`, `PhonePrefixPipe`
- Exported validator: `phoneMinLengthValidator`
